msgctxt "seo_title"
msgid "Tell Meta: Keep Encryption for Instagram Messages"
msgstr "Dites-le à Meta : continuez à chiffrer les messages Instagram"

msgctxt "search_description"
msgid ""
"Meta has quietly said it will end support for encrypted messaging on Instagram in a matter of weeks. Encryption helps ensure that what your messages stay between you and the person with whom you're communicating. When end-to-end encryption is enabled, no one – not even Meta – can snoop on you.\r"
"<br/> <br/>Right now, hundreds of millions of people use Instagram to message friends, family, and communities. Privacy should be a default feature of the technology we rely on every day – not an optional extra, and not something that quietly disappears. That's why we're asking Meta to reverse its decision and continue to support encryption on Instagram."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "title"
msgid "Tell Meta: Keep Encryption for Instagram Messages"
msgstr "Dites-le à Meta : continuez à chiffrer les messages Instagram"

msgctxt "body.55eff7a4-c93e-4263-b68f-a8aad68cb156"
msgid ""
"Meta has quietly said it will end support for encrypted messaging on Instagram in a matter of weeks. Encryption helps ensure that your messages stay between you and the person with whom you're "
"communicating. When end-to-end encryption is enabled, no one – not even Meta – can snoop on you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.55eff7a4-c93e-4263-b68f-a8aad68cb156"
msgid ""
"Right now, hundreds of millions of people use Instagram to message friends, family, and communities. Privacy should be a default feature of the technology we rely on every day – not an optional "
"extra, and not something that quietly disappears. <b>That's why we're asking Meta to reverse its decision and continue to support encryption on Instagram.</b>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.55eff7a4-c93e-4263-b68f-a8aad68cb156"
msgid ""
"Mozilla supporters have successfully forced Meta to change its apps' policies to support privacy before. <b>If enough people add their names to our petition, we can do it again – and this time, "
"we'll protect encryption on Instagram.</b>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "signed_header"
msgid "Thanks for signing our petition to keep Instagram messages encrypted! Can you add a donation?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "signed_body"
msgid ""
"Privacy should be a default feature of the technology we rely on every day – not an optional extra, and not something that quietly disappears. Will you add a donation to help keep the Internet open "
"and secure?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "share_header"
msgid "Share this with at least one other person"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "share_body"
msgid ""
"We know that Meta responds to public pressure when it comes to privacy on its apps. The more people who sign this petition to keep encryption on Instagram, the more likely we are to win. Can you "
"share this petition?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "thank_you_header"
msgid "All done here!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "thank_you_body"
msgid ""
"Mozilla is a nonprofit organization fighting for a healthy internet, where privacy is included by design and you have more control over your personal information. We depend on contributions from "
"people like you to carry out this work. Thank you for helping us!"
msgstr ""
"Mozilla est une organisation à but non lucratif qui se bat pour un Internet sain et sûr, où la confidentialité est intégrée à la conception et qui vous offre un contrôle accru sur vos informations "
"personnelles. Nous comptons sur les contributions de personnes comme vous pour mener à bien ce travail. Merci pour votre aide !"
